             External Posting Title
            Sr. Data Scientist
             Job Description
            Biogen is looking for a Senior Data Scientist to join our Data Science team in our Digital Health Technology and Data Science organization. As a member of the Data Science team, you will be tasked with weaving structured and unstructured data together from across Biogen to help answer some of our biggest questions.
            You will work directly with different teams across Biogen on different problems. Many times you will be part of a cross function team, which will require deeper understanding of complex problems.
            The background for this position is either a Scientist with a heavy analytics and data science background, or a Computer Scientist / Engineer who has been focused on Analytics and Data Science initiatives.
            You will be exposed to many different types of data and technology. This is a great position for someone who wants to be part of the “Data Revolution”. This position is located in in Cambridge, MA.
